#

Easy White Bread

40 min
$2.5
120 kcal
Difficulty: 20%
Servings: 12

Allergens:

Gluten

Dietary Tags:

VegetarianNut-Free

Cuisine:

American

Course:

Bread

Tags:

BreadBakingEasy

Description

Warm, fresh white bread that’s soft on the inside and has a golden crust.

Ingredients

  • all-purpose flour: 4 cups
  • warm water: 1 1/2 cups
  • sugar: 2 tablespoons
  • salt: 1 teaspoon
  • active dry yeast: 2 tablespoons
  • vegetable oil: 2 tablespoons
